Wake up. Lotus isn't the top guild on the server anymore and if you think us newbies in Wraith are going to get stuck in PoP because all of us are stuck till adequate spoilers are published while the only ppl blessed with any intelligence on the server (aka Lotus Cult) can conqueor the content, you are in for a  rude awakening.<br>
